{
  "page": "Wedding tourney at Whitewalls",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/bf/Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/300px-Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"306\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/bf/Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/450px-Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/bf/Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg/600px-Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Daemon_II_Blackfyre_by_Riotarttherite.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">Daemon II Blackfyre</a> as \"John the Fiddler\", by Riotarttherite ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>wedding tourney at Whitewalls</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aerys_i.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> held by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ambrose_Butterwell\" title=\"Ambrose Butterwell\">Ambrose Butterwell</a> to celebrate his second marriage to <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Butterwell\" title=\"Lady Butterwell\">the daughter</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Frey\" title=\"Lord Frey\">Lord Frey</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">212&#160;AC</a>. It was held at <a href=\"/index.php/Whitewalls\" title=\"Whitewalls\">Whitewalls</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> and was the grounds for the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"Second Blackfyre Rebellion\">Second Blackfyre Rebellion</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Tully_(successor_of_Medgar)\" title=\"Lord Tully (successor of Medgar)\">Lord Tully</a>, Ambrose's liege lord, was invited to the wedding tourney but declined to attend.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#The_Joust\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">The Joust</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Known_Attendees\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Attendees</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quote\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quote</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Joust\">The Joust</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Joust\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The format was a standard knock-out tournament. Two knights entered the lists under false names, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Duncan the Tall</a> as the \"Gallows Knight\", a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">Daemon II Blackfyre</a> as \"John the Fiddler\", a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a>. The prize for the winner was supposed to have been Lord Butterwell's <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon_egg\" title=\"Dragon egg\">dragon egg</a>, but it was stolen before it could be awarded.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Secondary prizes were to be thirty <a href=\"/index.php/Currency\" title=\"Currency\">golden dragons</a> for the runner-up and ten golden dragons for each knight defeated in the previous round.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The tourney ended prematurely when a royalist army led by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Bloodraven</a> arrived to suppress the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Blackfyre_Rebellion\" title=\"Second Blackfyre Rebellion\">Second Blackfyre Rebellion</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/32px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/48px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/64px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Paege\" title=\"House Paege\"><img alt=\"House Paege.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/83/House_Paege.svg/32px-House_Paege.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/83/House_Paege.svg/48px-House_Paege.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/83/House_Paege.svg/64px-House_Paege.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Franklyn_Frey\" title=\"Franklyn Frey\">Franklyn Frey</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harbert_Paege\" title=\"Harbert Paege\">Harbert Paege</a> (5 tilts)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\"><img alt=\"Quentyn Ball.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/32px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/48px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/64px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\">Glendon Flowers</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Argrave_the_Defiant\" title=\"Argrave the Defiant\">Argrave the Defiant</a> (1 tilt)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Caswell\" title=\"House Caswell\"><img alt=\"House Caswell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/32px-House_Caswell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/48px-House_Caswell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/2a/House_Caswell.svg/64px-House_Caswell.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/Kyle_the_Cat\" title=\"Kyle the Cat\"><img alt=\"Kyle the Cat.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/57/Kyle_the_Cat.svg/32px-Kyle_the_Cat.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/57/Kyle_the_Cat.svg/48px-Kyle_the_Cat.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/57/Kyle_the_Cat.svg/64px-Kyle_the_Cat.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Caswell\" title=\"Joffrey Caswell\">Joffrey Caswell</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Kyle_the_Cat\" title=\"Kyle the Cat\">Kyle the Cat</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Misty_Moor\" title=\"Misty Moor\">Misty Moor</a> (1 tilt)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\"><img alt=\"Uthor.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/32px-Uthor.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/48px-Uthor.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/64px-Uthor.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\"><img alt=\"Gallows Knight.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Gallows_Knight.svg/32px-Gallows_Knight.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Gallows_Knight.svg/48px-Gallows_Knight.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Gallows_Knight.svg/64px-Gallows_Knight.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a> defeated the <a href=\"/index.php/Duncan_the_Tall\" title=\"Duncan the Tall\">Gallows Knight</a> (1 tilt)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Smallwood\" title=\"House Smallwood\"><img alt=\"House Smallwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/32px-House_Smallwood.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/48px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/80/House_Smallwood.svg/64px-House_Smallwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> The nephew of <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Smallwood\" title=\"Lord Smallwood\">Lord Smallwood</a> broke his wrist while facing an unnamed opponent<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Risley\" title=\"House Risley\"><img alt=\"House Risley.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Risley.svg/32px-House_Risley.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5b/House_Risley.svg/48px-House_Risley.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5b/House_Risley.svg/64px-House_Risley.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Eden_Risley\" title=\"Eden Risley\">Eden Risley</a> had his leg crushed beneath his horse while facing an unnamed opponent<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/32px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/48px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/64px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Frey\" title=\"Addam Frey\">Addam Frey</a> defeated an unnamed rider<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafaddam_frey.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafaddam_frey.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\"><img alt=\"Uthor.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/32px-Uthor.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/48px-Uthor.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/64px-Uthor.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/32px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/48px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/64px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a> defeated Ser Addam Frey<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafaddam_frey.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafaddam_frey.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\"><img alt=\"Quentyn Ball.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/32px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/48px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/64px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cockshaw\" title=\"House Cockshaw\"><img alt=\"House Cockshaw.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/26/House_Cockshaw.svg/32px-House_Cockshaw.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/26/House_Cockshaw.svg/48px-House_Cockshaw.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/26/House_Cockshaw.svg/64px-House_Cockshaw.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser Glendon Flowers defeated Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Cockshaw\" title=\"Alyn Cockshaw\">Alyn Cockshaw</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\"><img alt=\"John the Fiddler.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/John_the_Fiddler.svg/32px-John_the_Fiddler.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/John_the_Fiddler.svg/48px-John_the_Fiddler.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dd/John_the_Fiddler.svg/64px-John_the_Fiddler.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\"><img alt=\"House Frey.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/32px-House_Frey.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/48px-House_Frey.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/da/House_Frey.svg/64px-House_Frey.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">John the Fiddler</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Franklyn_Frey\" title=\"Franklyn Frey\">Franklyn Frey</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\"><img alt=\"Quentyn Ball.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/32px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/48px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/64px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Costayne\" title=\"House Costayne\"><img alt=\"House Costayne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/House_Costayne.svg/32px-House_Costayne.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/House_Costayne.svg/48px-House_Costayne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/House_Costayne.svg/64px-House_Costayne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser Glendon Flowers defeated <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Costayne_(Aerys_I)\" title=\"Lord Costayne (Aerys I)\">Lord Costayne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\"><img alt=\"Quentyn Ball.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/32px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/48px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/64px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Boggs\" title=\"House Boggs\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/32px-None.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/48px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/64px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser Glendon Flowers defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Mortimer_Boggs\" title=\"Mortimer Boggs\">Mortimer Boggs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tommard_Heddle\" title=\"Tommard Heddle\"><img alt=\"Tommard Heddle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/Tommard_Heddle.svg/32px-Tommard_Heddle.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/Tommard_Heddle.svg/48px-Tommard_Heddle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7d/Tommard_Heddle.svg/64px-Tommard_Heddle.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Charlton\" title=\"House Charlton\"><img alt=\"House Charlton.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/22/House_Charlton.svg/32px-House_Charlton.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/22/House_Charlton.svg/48px-House_Charlton.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/22/House_Charlton.svg/64px-House_Charlton.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tommard_Heddle\" title=\"Tommard Heddle\">Tommard Heddle</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Clarence_Charlton\" title=\"Clarence Charlton\">Clarence Charlton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\"><img alt=\"Uthor.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/32px-Uthor.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/48px-Uthor.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/64px-Uthor.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bulwer\" title=\"House Bulwer\"><img alt=\"House Bulwer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/32px-House_Bulwer.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/48px-House_Bulwer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8d/House_Bulwer.svg/64px-House_Bulwer.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Buford_Bulwer\" title=\"Buford Bulwer\">Theomore Bulwer</a> (5 tilts)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\"><img alt=\"John the Fiddler.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/John_the_Fiddler.svg/32px-John_the_Fiddler.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/John_the_Fiddler.svg/48px-John_the_Fiddler.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dd/John_the_Fiddler.svg/64px-John_the_Fiddler.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Galtry_the_Green\" title=\"Galtry the Green\"><img alt=\"Galtry the Green.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/32px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/48px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/Galtry_the_Green.svg/64px-Galtry_the_Green.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">John the Fiddler</a> defeated Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Galtry_the_Green\" title=\"Galtry the Green\">Galtry the Green</a> (10 tilts)</li></ul>\n<p>The tourney was then interrupted by claims that a thief had stolen the dragon egg. The next tilt would have been:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Tommard_Heddle\" title=\"Tommard Heddle\"><img alt=\"Tommard Heddle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/Tommard_Heddle.svg/32px-Tommard_Heddle.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7d/Tommard_Heddle.svg/48px-Tommard_Heddle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7d/Tommard_Heddle.svg/64px-Tommard_Heddle.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\"><img alt=\"Uthor.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/32px-Uthor.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/48px-Uthor.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/Uthor.svg/64px-Uthor.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tommard_Heddle\" title=\"Tommard Heddle\">Tommard Heddle</a> versus Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Uthor_Underleaf\" title=\"Uthor Underleaf\">Uthor Underleaf</a></li></ul>\n<p>A <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a> was then held to determine the guilt or innocence of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\">Glendon Flowers</a> in the theft of the dragon egg:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\"><img alt=\"Quentyn Ball.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/32px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/48px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/1/15/Quentyn_Ball.svg/64px-Quentyn_Ball.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackfyre\" title=\"House Blackfyre\"><img alt=\"House Blackfyre 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Blackfyre_2.svg/32px-House_Blackfyre_2.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/a/a3/House_Blackfyre_2.svg/48px-House_Blackfyre_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/a/a3/House_Blackfyre_2.svg/64px-House_Blackfyre_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Glendon_Flowers\" title=\"Glendon Flowers\">Glendon Flowers</a> defeated the accuser, <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">Daemon II Blackfyre</a> (1 tilt)</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Attendees\">Known Attendees</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Wedding_tourney_at_Whitewalls&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Attendees\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Butterwell\" title=\"House Butterwell\"><img alt=\"House Butterwell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Butterwell.svg/32px-House_Butterwell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Butterwell.svg/48px-House_Butterwell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8d/House_Butterwell.svg/64px-House_Butterwell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ambrose_Butterwell\" title=\"Ambrose Butterwell\">Ambrose Butterwell</a><br /></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Butterwell\" title=\"House Butterwell\"><img alt=\"House Butterwell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Butterwell.svg/32px-House_Butterwell.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8d/House_Butterwell.svg/48px-House_Butterwell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thum